vote.title: An ordinance granting renewal of a revocable license to Big Outdoor Texas, LLC, for the use of approximately 360 square feet of aerial space to occupy, maintain and utilize the existing 12 lights that illuminate a supergraphic façade over a portion of Pacific Avenue right-of-way located near its intersection with Griffin Street - Revenue: General Fund $2,653.00 annually, plus the $20.00 ordinance publication fee
